              <header class="style1">
                <h2>The Top Opioid Affected States: Michigan</h2>
              </header>
              <a href="#" class="image featured"> <img src="../images/michigan01.jpg"

                  alt="Picture of Michigan"> </a> <br>
              <p><b>Overdose Deaths</b></p>
              <p>In 2015, the state of Michigan had a recorded 1,980 overdoses
                that resulted in death, 66% (1,309) of those deaths were caused
                by opioid overdoses. </p>
              <p>Michigan has the 15th highest percentage of teenagers aged 12
                to 17 that have used illicit drugs. It has the 13th highest
                percentage of teenagers in grades 9 to 12 who were offered,
                sold, or given and illegal drug on school property in the last
                year. It also has the 10th highest number of opioid pain
                reliever prescriptions per 100 residents.</p>
            </article>
            <a href="#" class="image featured"> </a>
            <div class="row 150%"><a href="#" class="image featured"> </a>
              <div class="4u 12u(mobile)"><a href="#" class="image featured"> </a>
                <section class="box"><a href="#" class="image featured"></a>
                  <header>
                    <h2>Saginaw</h2>
                  </header>
                  <a href="#" class="image featured"><img src="../images/michigan02.jpg"

                      alt="Picture of Saginaw"></a>
                  <p>As of July 2016, the police force in Saginaw was sseverely
                    cut back and as a result crime rates have increased.</p>
                </section>
              </div>
              <div class="4u 12u(mobile)">
                <section class="box">
                  <header> <br>
                    <h2>Flint</h2>
                  </header>
                  <a href="#" class="image featured"><img src="../images/michigan03.jpg"

                      alt="Picture of Flint"></a>
                  <p>In July of 2016, the rape cases in Flint were at an all
                    time high. Budget cuts have forced huge layoffs in the
                    police force and they simply can't keep up with the crime in
                    the city.</p>
                </section>
              </div>
              <div class="4u 12u(mobile)">
                <section class="box">
                  <header> <br>
                    <h2>Detroit</h2>
                  </header>
                  <a href="#" class="image featured"><img src="../images/michigan04.jpg"

                      alt="Picture of Detroit"></a>
                  <p>All the rumors are true, Detroit is still the most
                    dangerous city in the <em>Country</em>. Every year 2137 out
                    of every 100,000 resident is arrested for a violent offense.</p>
                </section>
